news.headline: RBC Downgrades Lennar on Margin Pressures

news.article_text:
This article first appeared on GuruFocus.

Lennar (NYSE:LEN) is starting to look like a tougher story, at least in the eyes of RBC Capital Markets. The firm downgraded the homebuilder to Underperform, arguing that margin pressure is not going away anytime soon.

Shares reacted quickly. Lennar stock fell 4.6% during Wednesday's regular session after the company reported weaker than expected Q4 earnings and issued soft Q1 guidance. The slide continued after hours, with the stock down another 0.6%.
